SELECT project_name, member_name, SUM(actual_duration) AS total_actual_duration FROM projects JOIN project_team ON projects.project_id = project_team.project_id JOIN team_members ON project_team.member_id = team_members.member_id JOIN tasks ON team_members.member_id = tasks.milestone_id GROUP BY project_name, member_name HAVING SUM(actual_duration) > 20;
